Blue
====

Blue is a content management system foundation used to create adminable websites.


Install
=======

0. Pre-req, install rails engines if not already.

1. Add as a submodule
git submodule add git@github.com:bluespan/blue.git vendor/plugins/blue
git submodule init
git submodule update

2. Include routes in your applications config/routes.rb
map.from_plugin :blue

3. Copy over initializers/blue.rb to config/initializers

4. Link plugin assets
ln -s vendor/plugins/assets public/plugin_assets/blue

